[207.465205, "o", "\u001b[2J\u001b[3J\u001b[H\u001b[38;2;215;119;87mв•ӯв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв•®\u001b[39m\r\n\u001b[38;2;215;119;87mв”Ӯ\u001b[39m \u001b[38;2;215;119;87mвң»\u001b[39m Welcome to \u001b[1mClaude Code\u001b[22m!                             \u001b[38;2;215;119;87mв”Ӯ\u001b[39m\r\n\u001b[38;2;215;119;87mв”Ӯ\u001b[39m                                                       \u001b[38;2;215;119;87mв”Ӯ\u001b[39m\r\n\u001b[38;2;215;119;87mв”Ӯ\u001b[39m   \u001b[3m\u001b[38;2;153;153;153m/help for help, /status for your current setup\u001b[39m\u001b[23m      \u001b[38;2;215;119;87mв”Ӯ\u001b[39m\r\n\u001b[38;2;215;119;87mв”Ӯ\u001b[39m                                                       \u001b[38;2;215;119;87mв”Ӯ\u001b[39m\r\n\u001b[38;2;215;119;87mв”Ӯ\u001b[39m   \u001b[38;2;153;153;153mcwd: /Users/robertgrayson/playground/nathan_for_us\u001b[39m  \u001b[38;2;215;119;87mв”Ӯ\u001b[39m\r\n\u001b[38;2;215;119;87mв•°в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җ"]
[207.466165, "o", "в”Җв”Җв•Ҝ\u001b[39m\r\n\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;153;153;153m>\u001b[39m \u001b[38;2;153;153;153mlets rearrange how the skeets page works. Currently, it just displays a list. Let's make a 'card' for each skeet,\u001b[39m\r\n  \u001b[38;2;153;153;153m and try to display as many as we can on the page in a mosaic without cramping them too much. make the mosaic \u001b[39m\r\n  \u001b[38;2;153;153;153mpiece its own component and encompass the logic that is already present there. for this we will want to stick to \u001b[39m\r\n  \u001b[38;2;153;153;153m4 in a row max. it should be really readable and look like a hodge podge of posts from a bunch of people\u001b[39m\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;255;255;255mвҸә\u001b[39m I'll help you rearrange the skeets page to use a card-based mosaic layout. Let me start by examining the current\r\n  implementation.\r\n  вҺҝ В вҳҗ Examine current skeets page implementation\r\n     вҳҗ Create new skeet card component\r\n     вҳҗ Update skeets page to use mosaic layout with max 4 per row\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;78;186;101mвҸә\u001b[39m \u001b[1mRead\u001b[22m(lib/nathan_for_us_web/live/skeets_live.ex)\r\n  вҺҝ В Read"]
[207.466336, "o", " \u001b[1m303\u001b[22m lines \u001b[38;2;153;153;153m(ctrl+r to expand)\u001b[39m\r\n  вҺҝ В \u001b[38;2;78;186;101mвҳ’ \u001b[9mExamine current skeets page implementation\u001b[39m\u001b[29m\r\n     \u001b[1m\u001b[38;2;177;185;249mвҳҗ Create new skeet card component\u001b[39m\u001b[22m\r\n     вҳҗ Update skeets page to use mosaic layout with max 4 per row\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;255;255;255mвҸә\u001b[39m Now I'll create a new skeet card component and update the layout to use a mosaic with max 4 per row:\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;153;153;153mвҸә\u001b[39m \u001b[1mWrite\u001b[22m(lib/nathan_for_us_web/components/skeet_card.ex)\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;215;119;87mВ·\u001b[39m \u001b[38;2;215;119;87mArrangingвҖҰ \u001b[38;2;153;153;153m(0s В· вҡ’\u001b[39m \u001b[38;2;153;153;153m0 tokens В· \u001b[1mesc \u001b[22mto interrupt)\u001b[39m\r\n\r\n\u001b[2m\u001b[38;2;136;136;136mв•ӯв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җ"]
